\p 
\v 5 “\w I|strong="H3605"\w*'ll \w do|strong="H6213"\w* \w everything|strong="H3605"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w told|strong="H6213"\w* \w me|strong="H6213"\w*,” said Ruth.
